Proposition 8 passed.

00:03:58.182 --> 00:04:00.810
It was the most controversial
state issue on the ballot.

00:04:00.885 --> 00:04:03.354
You know I'm talking
about Proposition number 8,

00:04:03.421 --> 00:04:05.787
