all riding the same bus

00:04:26.577 --> 00:04:29.342
and they, too,
won't sit in the back.

00:04:29.413 --> 00:04:32.383
I am disappointed in the
African American community,

00:04:32.450 --> 00:04:35.476
but hopeful that
they will revisit it

00:04:35.553 --> 00:04:37.680
and see us also as
a civil rights movement.

00:04:37.755 --> 00:04:41.123
—l was on the front lines
in California,

00:04:41.192 --> 00:04:45.857
fighting against
Proposition 8 and,

00:04:45.930 --> 00:04:48.558
a few days later, my phone
started ringing more,

00:04:48.632 --> 00:04:52.194
to say "How could you
let this happen?"

00:04:52.269 --> 00:04:54.261
And I was like
"Excuse me’?

00:04:54.338 --> 00:04:58.673
Are you trying
to blame me

00:04:58.743 --> 00:05:01.769
for the passage of
Proposition 8'?"

00:05:01.846 --> 00:05:05.043
—It was a very
divisive campaign.

00:05:05.116 --> 00:05:07.482
Millions of dollars

00:05:07.551 --> 00:05:10.248
came into that campaign

00:05:10.321 --> 00:05:11.811
from the Mormon church

00:05:11.889 --> 00:05:15.382
