and evangelical churches

00:05:15.459 --> 00:05:18.361
to reach out
with great effort

00:05:18.429 --> 00:05:21.865
to communities of color.

00:05:21.932 --> 00:05:24.424
Those in favor of Proposition 8
aggressively reached out

00:05:24.502 --> 00:05:26.129
to African American clergy,

00:05:26.203 --> 00:05:29.036
