is not monolithic.

00:05:48.759 --> 00:05:50.989
We're just like
any other community.

00:05:51.061 --> 00:05:52.495
To make that assumption was,
I think,

00:05:52.563 --> 00:05:54.554
a critical error
in strategy.

00:05:58.202 --> 00:06:01.604
—Define "marriage".

00:06:01.672 --> 00:06:02.867
