00:06:04.375 --> 00:06:06.275
the union between
a man and a woman.

00:06:06.343 --> 00:06:08.812
[Applause]
—Now, for me, as a Christian —-

00:06:08.879 --> 00:06:10.210
For me —-

00:06:10.281 --> 00:06:14.377
[Applause]

00:06:14.452 --> 00:06:16.113
