what we need to do."

00:24:41.524 --> 00:24:44.824
So we do need to have
a message out there again

00:24:44.894 --> 00:24:47.454
to people who don't understand
why they can't get married

00:24:47.530 --> 00:24:49.931
or why they should get married
and to understand

00:24:49.999 --> 00:24:52.491
those thousand rights
that we get deprived.

00:24:52.569 --> 00:24:54.298
—But you can't argue
with them

00:24:54.370 --> 00:24:55.736
because they'll go
straight into

00:24:55.805 --> 00:24:57.296
economics, education,
—HeaIth, voting.

00:24:57.373 --> 00:25:00.206
employment, and health,
and those things, to them —-

00:25:00.276 --> 00:25:02.711
their argument is those
are more important to me

00:25:02.779 --> 00:25:04.975
than you telling me I have to
go tell this white man

00:25:05.048 --> 00:25:07.312
that we are interested
in getting married.

00:25:07.383 --> 00:25:10.478
When people say those things,
"It's not a black issue,"

00:25:10.553 --> 00:25:11.987
we have to stop them
from saying that,

00:25:12.055 --> 00:25:14.615
that maybe it's not your issue,
but, as a community,

00:25:14.691 --> 00:25:16.352
it is our issue because
there are lots of people

00:25:16.426 --> 00:25:20.488
in our community who want
to engage in gay marriage.

00:25:20.563 --> 00:25:23.965
I agree with both of you.
The one thing I would say

00:25:24.033 --> 00:25:28.163
